    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 factors and determined that the model is suitable for its intended use. Despite three factors (Software quality assurance, Numerical code verification, Output comparison) achieving level 1 against a required level 2, the team judged the overall evidence sufficient given the medium model influence and the availability of supporting experimental data across all five operating points. The decision is Accepted at Medium assurance level.",
